@keen brought Camp Jasper to Paris Fashion Week, transforming a traditional showroom into a space built around outdoor culture, community, and the brand's climbing-inspired Jasper silhouette.⁠
⁠
Alongside a curated archive tracing Jasper's evolution since 2008, the space featured live customization, community runs, birdwatching, and a first look at the next chapter of KEEN Lifestyle. Tap the link in bio to read the full story.⁠

